data.text:
she smiles sun at me

slipping out
of her clothes
in the shade
of a marula tree
she finds solace

she wades in the river
in the silt
between her toes
she finds patience

she dives under
finding forgiveness

floating
she finds direction

and I find
beauty
as I watch her

#vss365
